(285, 'BIBL', 'BIBL-4803', '4', '3', 'Ministry Practicum', 'On-site practical service in a local congregation by invitation and under the oversight of the elders and in conjunction with the local minister(s) and a faculty supervisor. The course includes readings, a journal, and a thorough evaluation. Non-textual. This course is normally offered every semester.'),
