(530, 'CENG', 'CENG-3203', '3', '3', 'Intro to Microprocessors', 'Prerequisite: ENGR-2544. Introduction to the architecture and programming of microprocessors and microcontrollers. Computer organization, addressing modes, assembly language programming techniques and interfacing. Lecture - 3 hours. This class is normally offered in the fall semester.'),
