(554, 'CENG', 'CENG-5113', '5', '3', 'Software and Network Engineering', 'A study of advanced computer network systems design issues. Examination of the prominent protocols and standards for wired and wireless local area networks and the wireless Internet. Students cannot receive credit for both CENG-4123 and CENG-5113.'),
