(1097, 'EDUC', 'EDUC-4422', '4', '2', 'Elem Music Methods', 'Prerequisites: EDUC-3213; Admission to Teacher Education. Methods for teaching general music in the elementary school. Course requirements include 18 hours of field experience. This course is normally offered in the fall semester odd years.'),
