(1243, 'ELEM', 'ELEM-4900P', '4', 'P', 'Intermediate Practicum', 'An intermediate grade (4-5) practicum, 60 hours. The focus of the practicum is for the candidate to construct and present lessons in literacy, math, science, and social studies at the intermediate level. Supervision and assessment of the candidate will be conducted by a university supervisor and the classroom teacher. This course is normally offered in the spring semester. Concurrent enrollment ELEM-4242, ELEM-4342, ELEM-4433, ELEM-4443.'),
(1244, 'ELEM', 'ELEM-4901', '4', '1', 'Independent Practicum', 'An intermediate grade (4-5) practicum, 60 hours. The focus of the practicum is for the candidate to construct and present lessons in literacy, math, science, and social studies at the intermediate level. Supervision and assessment of the candidate will be conducted by a university supervisor and the classroom teacher. This course is normally offered in the spring semester. Concurrent enrollment ELEM-4242, ELEM-4342, ELEM-4433, ELEM-4443.'),
