(1295, 'ENGL', 'ENGL-3673', '3', '3', 'Amer Lit Surv I', 'Prerequisite: ENGL-1213 and ENGL-2223 with a grade of C or better. Non-majors by permission only. A study of early American literature from the writings of the explorers and colonists through Edgar Allan Poe. This course is normally offered in the fall semester of even numbered years.'),
