(1298, 'ENGL', 'ENGL-3773', '3', '3', 'Amer Lit Surv II', 'Prerequisite: ENGL-1213 and ENGL-2223 with a grade of C or better. Non-majors by permission only. A study of the major American authors and literary movements from the postbellum era to the twenty-first century. This course is normally offered in the spring semester of odd numbered years.'),
