(1402, 'ENGR', 'ENGR-5003', '5', '3', 'Found of Tech Ethics and Values Values', 'Theories of engineering ethics and values. Ethical theory from a Christian viewpoint. Impact of technology on society. Individual options and obligations for action. Case studies will be used to study a range of issues including environment, safety, honesty, organizational communication, quality control and product liability.'),
