(1718, 'GNSC', 'GNSC-4850', '4', '0', 'Service Learning Project', 'Provides an opportunity for learning in a service environment. Students select a service project and work with a faculty mentor to develop the academic background, assignments, and reflection to create a unique learning opportunity. One hour of class time each week will be devoted to meeting with mentors and other students to discuss the project. Variable credit (1-t3 hours) will be given based on the number of service hours and academic responsibilities. This course is offered as needed.'),
