(1886, 'HONR', 'HONR-2113', '2', '3', 'The Quest for Meaning: Christ', 'A course based on the supposition that Jesus Christ provides the best solution to persistent puzzles of life: Why am I here?\" \"What is worth doing?\" \"How can I live a good life?\" \"Where am I going?\" To see Jesus\' answers in context'),
