(2317, 'MKTG', 'MKTG-5713', '5', '3', 'The Sales Process and Ethical Influence', 'Sales is a master\'s level, marketing-track course aimed at educating professionsl in the use of sales principles and techniques to ethically persuade and influence. Though part of the course provides insight into the selling profession, it essentially uses the sales process as a backdrop is to train students in the process of selling and its application in numerous aspects of marketing and marketing management. Understanding the process has transfer value\" in terms of negotiations'),
