(2851, 'SDEV', 'SDEV-2011', '2', '1', 'Discovering Your Strengths', 'This course is designed to serve the needs of students who have not yet chosen a college major or students who question whether or not their current major is the right one for them. This class allows students to discover more fully their strengths and interests and, as a result, to identify appropriate careers and majors it also helps students develop high performance skills such as critical thinking.'),
