(2853, 'SDEV', 'SDEV-2113', '2', '3', 'Success in College and Life', 'This course assists students in transitioning into and out of university life. The class acquaints students with techniques that encourage student success, improve and refine academic skills, and develop skills and attitudes needed to achieve educational and personal goals. This course is normally offered in the fall and spring semesters.'),
